Where do you think you're sitting?

887
00:48:03,787 --> 00:48:04,801
Mom.

888
00:48:05,948 --> 00:48:07,294
It's okay if I stand.

889
00:48:08,124 --> 00:48:10,407
I have nothing to say so
I don't care if you stand there or not.

890
00:48:10,442 --> 00:48:11,064
Mom.

891
00:48:11,099 --> 00:48:12,622
Don't be like that.

892
00:48:13,574 --> 00:48:14,205
Mother.

893
00:48:14,388 --> 00:48:16,695
Who are you calling mother?

894
00:48:19,588 --> 00:48:20,412
Mother.

895
00:48:21,217 --> 00:48:23,315
I have something to say today.

896
00:48:23,350 --> 00:48:25,077
Aigoo... really...

897
00:48:25,412 --> 00:48:26,350
Why are you doing this?

898
00:48:26,385 --> 00:48:27,481
Unni, sit.

899
00:48:27,516 --> 00:48:28,257
Sit down please.

900
00:48:28,292 --> 00:48:30,358
Sit, sit, sit.

901
00:48:39,444 --> 00:48:42,082
I know I don't have the right.

902
00:48:42,982 --> 00:48:44,883
I don't have anything to offer now,

903
00:48:45,601 --> 00:48:48,857
but I will work my hardest to make noona happy.

904
00:48:49,481 --> 00:48:51,668
You who don't have anything right now?

905
00:48:51,903 --> 00:48:54,450
So why did you come to see me?

906
00:48:54,485 --> 00:48:54,929
Mom...

907
00:48:54,964 --> 00:48:56,242
You shut your mouth.

908
00:48:57,306 --> 00:48:59,632
Okay, fine.

909
00:49:00,267 --> 00:49:02,057
What did your parents say?

910
00:49:02,292 --> 00:49:03,323
Do they like my daughter?

911
00:49:03,358 --> 00:49:04,766
They were not shocked?

912
00:49:05,201 --> 00:49:06,669
I haven't told them yet.

913
00:49:07,905 --> 00:49:09,634
Because you are first, mother.

914
00:49:10,157 --> 00:49:12,758
I will take care of my parents.

915
00:49:12,993 --> 00:49:15,376
So noona will be okay.
Don't worry.

916
00:49:15,411 --> 00:49:17,178
Oh really...

917
00:49:17,313 --> 00:49:18,942
There is nothing more to listen to.

918
00:49:19,077 --> 00:49:20,043
Mother.

919
00:49:20,378 --> 00:49:21,908
Mother, please I beg of you.

920
00:49:25,102 --> 00:49:27,535
It was a hard decision to make for both noona and me.

921
00:49:27,891 --> 00:49:29,269
And we thought over it a long time.

922
00:49:30,158 --> 00:49:34,166
Even if you object, please allow me
to do everything I can.

923
00:49:34,733 --> 00:49:36,806
You probably cannot make money right away.

924
00:49:37,341 --> 00:49:39,273
What do your parents do?

925
00:49:39,608 --> 00:49:41,993
Can they financially help you?

926
00:49:42,853 --> 00:49:45,496
My father is a elementary baseball team coach.

927
00:49:46,031 --> 00:49:48,735
And my mother owns a small gift shop.

928
00:49:50,654 --> 00:49:52,651
They will probably help us a little,

929
00:49:52,933 --> 00:49:55,496
but they worked hard to make me a baseball player.

930
00:49:56,079 --> 00:49:58,706
I want to do this marriage by my strength.

931
00:49:59,346 --> 00:50:00,305
How?

932
00:50:00,340 --> 00:50:01,274
By what?

933
00:50:01,309 --> 00:50:04,739
I'm working hard, so by next year I can make money.

934
00:50:04,774 --> 00:50:06,652
How can a student make money?

935
00:50:06,787 --> 00:50:08,612
Are you going to work part time at a grocery store?

936
00:50:08,747 --> 00:50:12,445
I am going to make money by throwing balls.

937
00:50:13,346 --> 00:50:14,452
I still...

938
00:50:15,004 --> 00:50:17,750
I still cannot tell you for sure,

939
00:50:18,455 --> 00:50:20,654
but I will not lean on noona.

940
00:50:20,863 --> 00:50:22,754
This I promise you.

941
00:50:22,889 --> 00:50:28,713
Look here, I really have nothing more to hear.

942
00:50:28,948 --> 00:50:32,657
I can understand that you are
a really nice and good person,

943
00:50:32,992 --> 00:50:36,569
but you cannot live this world
with just trying and promises.

944
00:50:36,804 --> 00:50:41,030
Even now your will is ahead but you are not giving me
anything that I can put my trust in.

945
00:50:42,304 --> 00:50:45,553
Today... I had a lot of things to tell you.

946
00:50:46,074 --> 00:50:48,083
Only hollow words, no more.

947
00:50:48,118 --> 00:50:49,898
Please let's stop.

948
00:50:51,804 --> 00:50:52,311
Mom.

949
00:50:52,346 --> 00:50:53,624
You keep still.

950
00:50:59,433 --> 00:51:03,858
Nan Hee, this is an account I made in your name.

951
00:51:04,686 --> 00:51:06,797
