30 year old and make you stay home.

954
00:51:17,074 --> 00:51:19,275
I cannot lock you in a room with a lock.

955
00:51:20,293 --> 00:51:22,907
You are not the type to listen to me.

956
00:51:23,142 --> 00:51:24,816
You... don't come here either.

957
00:51:25,677 --> 00:51:27,586
You cannot break up with that student.

958
00:51:27,821 --> 00:51:30,023
And I can not give my consent.

959
00:51:30,958 --> 00:51:35,276
Anyways, you went out to try living on your own.

960
00:51:35,311 --> 00:51:36,538
Let's cut our ties.

961
00:51:36,773 --> 00:51:38,724
Mother, please don't.

962
00:51:39,355 --> 00:51:41,447
We will not get married until you approve.

963
00:51:41,682 --> 00:51:43,209
Then will you break up?

964
00:51:44,812 --> 00:51:47,157
You both, tell me your answer right now.

965
00:51:47,392 --> 00:51:51,269
And you telling me to approve that answer
no matter what, is a threat right?

966
00:51:56,209 --> 00:51:57,531
Receive this.

967
00:51:58,025 --> 00:51:59,641
And let me go.

968
00:52:00,434 --> 00:52:02,432
Like you have things you want to do.

969
00:52:02,467 --> 00:52:05,741
I also had hopes for my children.

970
00:52:12,597 --> 00:52:13,418
Noona?

971
00:52:13,923 --> 00:52:14,637
Huh?

972
00:52:16,303 --> 00:52:21,104
In this world, there aren't a lot of things I can do.

973
00:52:22,303 --> 00:52:23,528
Me too.

974
00:52:25,405 --> 00:52:27,326
I feel really ashamed in front of you.

975
00:52:28,526 --> 00:52:33,197
I told you that I would be able to show
her that I'm a responsible person.

976
00:52:39,918 --> 00:52:41,072
But still,

977
00:52:41,407 --> 00:52:42,897
you can't get tired already.

978
00:53:04,513 --> 00:53:05,645
You came?

979
00:53:06,317 --> 00:53:08,770
Thanks. I will return it after dry cleaning it.

980
00:53:08,805 --> 00:53:11,616
It's okay. You got scolded a lot, right?

981
00:53:13,413 --> 00:53:14,519
Do you want me to help?

982
00:53:14,554 --> 00:53:15,871
Try to help convince ahjumma?

983
00:53:16,006 --> 00:53:17,687
Jun Joo said he will do it.

984
00:53:18,122 --> 00:53:20,872
He said he will go everyday until he gets approval.

985
00:53:22,855 --> 00:53:24,479
Hey look how it is soaked in sweat.

986
00:53:25,436 --> 00:53:27,061
He must have been really nervous.

987
00:53:42,678 --> 00:53:44,269
Unni, just go home.

988
00:53:44,304 --> 00:53:45,416
Open the door.

989
00:53:45,651 --> 00:53:47,729
Since before mom also... come later.

990
00:53:47,764 --> 00:53:50,851
I know that's why I came. Please open.

991
00:53:56,396 --> 00:53:57,237
Okay.

992
00:53:57,672 --> 00:53:59,165
This is good.

993
00:53:59,300 --> 00:54:02,112
I can just say whatever I want and then leave.

994
00:54:04,083 --> 00:54:08,400
The shirt Jung Joo wore was soaked with sweat.

995
00:54:10,154 --> 00:54:12,893
He must have been really nervous in front of you, mom.

996
00:54:13,928 --> 00:54:16,204
That Jung Joo you might not have believed in.

997
00:54:16,927 --> 00:54:21,273
But I'm thankful for Jung Joo trying so hard.

998
00:54:22,112 --> 00:54:23,948
Unsure future.

999
00:54:24,775 --> 00:54:30,606
Yeah I might just end up suffering
a lot like you said mom,  but...

1000
00:54:31,658 --> 00:54:34,323
But that does not matter at all to me, mom.

1001
00:54:35,332 --> 00:54:37,678
Because I love Jung Joo so much...

1002
00:54:39,709 --> 00:54:45,734
I want to live this unsure life with Jung Joo.

1003
00:54:48,507 --> 00:54:50,635
Jung Joo pitches...

1004
00:54:51,544 --> 00:54:54,082
Soars when I cheer for him.

1005
00:54:54,936 --> 00:54:57,621
Do you know how happy I am watching that?

1006
00:54:58,386 --> 00:55:00,793
Do you know how much he loves me?

1007
00:55:01,767 --> 00:55:06,298
Do you know how much he cares for me
who has nothing to really show?

1008
00:55:09,258 --> 00:55:16,543
It's the first time I found out that being 
loved by someone it's such a blessing.

1009
00:55:17,619 --> 00:55:20,568
I don't think I will have this again.

1010
00:55:20,803 --> 00:55:27,033
Receiving love or my heart shaking like this.

1011
00:55:27,168 --> 00:55:29,806
I think this will be the last time.

1012
00:55:30,741 --> 00:55:34,770
And that is why I can't... I can't fold it.

1013
00:55:41,024 --> 00:55:42,063
Mom.

1014
00:55:43,129 --> 00:55:45,372
I'm really sorry to you.

1015
00:55:46,692 --> 00:55:50,415
Because I haven't lived up to 
anything you had hoped for me.

1016
00:55:50,516 --> 00:55:51,867
I am truly sorry.

1017
00:55:52,975 --> 00:55:59,193
But to me, I don't need
the money you gave me right now,

1018
00:55:59,228 --> 00:56:00,907
but I need you.

1019
00:56:02,978 --> 00:56:05,986
When we say that we will not
get married without your consent,

1020
00:56:06,021 --> 00:56:10,561
that is not a threat but it's
because I need you right now.

1021
00:56:12,831 --> 00:56:14,827
Whether I live well or not.

1022
00:56:15,362 --> 00:56:19,099
I need a mom besides me who will cheer me.

1023
00:56:21,756 --> 00:56:24,704
If it turns out well, that will be the best.

1024
00:56:25,288 --> 00:56:26,681
But if it turns out bad,

1025
00:56:27,216 --> 00:56:31,904
If not, I need a mom beside me who will scold me for not listening to her.

1026
00:56:32,039 --> 00:56:34,908
Huh? Mom?

1027
00:56:36,096 --> 00:56:37,714
Mom?

1028
00:57:35,382 --> 00:57:37,829
He left this space for a Cy Young Award.

1029
00:57:37,864 --> 00:57:41,795
<i>Cy Young Award: an American award that
commemorates the great pitcher, Cy Young,</i>

1030
00:57:41,830 --> 00:57:47,074
<i>who pitched for 22 years in the major leagues by
giving the award to the best pitcher that year.</i>

1031
00:57:52,818 --> 00:57:53,419
<i>Noona!</i>

1032
00:57:53,454 --> 00:57:54,705
What? What?

1033
00:57:55,032 --> 00:57:56,422
That's a good thing?

1034
00:57:56,657 --> 00:57:57,779
Of course.

1035
00:57:58,014 --> 00:58:00,130
Now we must also tell your mom
that I will be able to make money.

1036
00:58:00,165 --> 00:58:02,144
You're an alternate player.

1037
00:58:02,179 --> 00:58:06,826
If you graduated, weren't you
supposed to go as the first pitcher?

1038
00:58:06,861 --> 00:58:10,721
I have to go to San Mi,
but even now they have too many pitchers.

1039
00:58:11,156 --> 00:58:13,482
The situation will not change must next year.

1040
00:58:13,517 --> 00:58:18,360
Instead, it is better to start playing to catch
my chance at moving up to first and making money.

1041
00:58:18,495 --> 00:58:19,733
But still...

1042
00:58:19,968 --> 00:58:21,562
Must you quit school?

1043
00:58:21,697 --> 00:58:23,818
I came to school to play baseball.

1044
00:58:24,053 --> 00:58:26,127
Playing baseball anywhere is the best thing.

1045
00:58:27,075 --> 00:58:28,713
That is so... but...

1046
00:58:29,060 --> 00:58:31,254
The pay will be really small.

1047
00:58:32,033 --> 00:58:34,131
Are you disappointed because I am an alternate?

1048
00:58:34,440 --> 00:58:37,892
Are you making a wrong decision because of marriage?

1049
00:58:38,399 --> 00:58:40,438
That worries me.

1050
00:58:40,795 --> 00:58:43,510
I can make ends meet until you graduate.

1051
00:58:43,645 --> 00:58:46,169
Thanks to marriage I'm making a good decision.

1052
00:58:46,304 --> 00:58:48,351
You aren't skipping practice right?

1053
00:58:48,486 --> 00:58:49,330
Of course.

1054
00:58:49,565 --> 00:58:52,073
No matter what, I stick to the workout schedule.

1055
00:58:52,493 --> 00:58:53,954
Good, you should.

1056
00:58:54,648 --> 00:58:55,566
Jung Joo.

1057
00:58:57,022 --> 00:59:00,943
Whatever decision you make, think of only yourself.

1058
00:59:01,216 --> 00:59:02,720
Make the decision selfishly.

1059
00:59:03,615 --> 00:59:05,961
That is the best for our future.

1060
00:59:06,472 --> 00:59:07,450
Okay?

1061
00:59:07,922 --> 00:59:10,394
Are you that nervous about me?

1062
00:59:11,300 --> 00:59:13,133
No, it's not that.

1063
00:59:15,586 --> 00:59:16,898
Eat, Jung Joo.

