00:59:21,759 --> 00:59:23,632
Eh, ball.

1065
00:59:27,751 --> 00:59:30,148
Wheew, strike.

1066
00:59:34,595 --> 00:59:37,676
It's been a long time since we have hugged like this.

1067
00:59:38,212 --> 00:59:41,308
After coming back from America,
it seems like a year has passed.

1068
00:59:41,443 --> 00:59:45,180
Yes, it was busy days.

1069
00:59:45,816 --> 00:59:47,917
Mother has to approve us.

1070
00:59:48,552 --> 00:59:52,971
If my mom is like this, what about your parents?

1071
00:59:53,549 --> 00:59:54,914
Don't worry.

1072
00:59:56,102 --> 00:59:57,060
Okay.

1073
00:59:57,317 --> 00:59:58,729
Let's forget for today.

1074
00:59:58,798 --> 01:00:00,795
Let's just love each other wholly.

1075
01:00:05,081 --> 01:00:08,385
This picture... I look at it a lot.

1076
01:00:09,070 --> 01:00:12,229
My mom calls it the Hall of Fame.

1077
01:00:12,513 --> 01:00:14,866
I will also help fill it now.

1078
01:00:16,111 --> 01:00:18,597
Jung Joo, but why did you put nothing here?

1079
01:00:18,732 --> 01:00:20,237
Did it used to hold something?

1080
01:00:20,272 --> 01:00:22,960
No, it's a place for the Cy Young Award.

1081
01:00:23,269 --> 01:00:24,881
Oh.

1082
01:00:25,829 --> 01:00:29,437
Ah, I wanted to give it to you
at the train station but I forgot.

1083
01:00:30,015 --> 01:00:30,848
Hmm?

1084
01:00:32,188 --> 01:00:34,009
It's the hat I wore while doing the test.

1085
01:00:35,025 --> 01:00:38,500
The object that witnesses how hard I've worked.

1086
01:00:39,142 --> 01:00:40,872
I thought of buying a ring,

1087
01:00:41,444 --> 01:00:43,458
but this has more meaning to me.

1088
01:00:44,151 --> 01:00:45,340
Thank you.

1089
01:00:45,575 --> 01:00:46,579
Too bad.

1090
01:00:47,130 --> 01:00:49,857
If I had given it to you then,
it would have been really romantic.

1091
01:00:52,800 --> 01:00:55,010
It really is the best present.

1092
01:00:55,897 --> 01:00:59,701
Noona, don't you feel unfair
being caught by a guy like me?

1093
01:00:59,736 --> 01:01:01,587
How can you say something like that?

1094
01:01:01,622 --> 01:01:03,371
You are the man I chose.

1095
01:01:04,585 --> 01:01:06,349
Lately I feel like I'm going through puberty.

1096
01:01:07,327 --> 01:01:11,962
Everyday thinking, am I only this much of a guy?

1097
01:01:13,500 --> 01:01:18,838
But still noona, even though I also
feel bad because I can't do much,

1098
01:01:19,195 --> 01:01:21,592
but I will definitely make it up to you for coming to me.

1099
01:01:21,827 --> 01:01:25,711
I will live hard as I tried hard when I wore that hat.

1100
01:01:27,911 --> 01:01:29,038
Ah,

1101
01:01:30,407 --> 01:01:32,911
I cannot think of anything better...

1102
01:01:34,116 --> 01:01:35,691
I just...

1103
01:01:35,726 --> 01:01:38,268
Wait a moment there is more.

1104
01:01:42,344 --> 01:01:46,449
This is the signed ball I practiced
with in elementary school.

1105
01:01:47,632 --> 01:01:50,225
It seems I tried to copy Kim Joo Ahn player's signature.

1106
01:01:50,630 --> 01:01:52,050
Who's that?

1107
01:01:52,542 --> 01:01:55,283
Noona, you know a lot of baseball
players because of me right?

1108
01:01:56,067 --> 01:01:56,881
Hmm.

1109
01:01:57,246 --> 01:01:59,903
Yes, I have gotten to know them because of you.

1110
01:02:00,038 --> 01:02:02,665
This player was the best 10 years ago.

1111
01:02:02,700 --> 01:02:03,966
He started as a alternate player,

1112
01:02:04,201 --> 01:02:07,518
but he led his team to the
championships and even got an M.V.P.

1113
01:02:07,896 --> 01:02:09,693
He even got offers from the major league.

1114
01:02:11,186 --> 01:02:12,130
He was my idol.

1115
01:02:12,265 --> 01:02:14,484
But how come I don't know.

1116
01:02:14,919 --> 01:02:16,727
After he got hurt, he had a surgery, and
because of that, he wasn't able to come back.

1117
01:02:17,078 --> 01:02:20,563
He has become a player no one knows about.

1118
01:02:21,129 --> 01:02:27,276
But he, who went to the top and fell
all the way to the bottom, is only 30 years old.

1119
01:02:28,972 --> 01:02:31,223
I'm in a very vicious world, noona.

1120
01:02:33,684 --> 01:02:37,494
And so I cannot guarantee what will happen to me.

1121
01:02:38,421 --> 01:02:41,007
I also cannot promise anything to your mother.

1122
01:02:42,434 --> 01:02:46,926
But still noona, if you are next to me I will try my best.

1123
01:02:47,415 --> 01:02:48,889
That I will promise.

1124
01:02:49,730 --> 01:02:50,840
Jung Joo.

1125
01:02:55,075 --> 01:02:56,705
I am so happy.

1126
01:02:58,137 --> 01:03:00,700
I am so happy that you are my man.

1127
01:03:02,023 --> 01:03:05,266
Let's love for a long time.

1128
01:03:06,127 --> 01:03:06,789
Hmm.

1129
01:03:06,426 --> 01:03:06,789
<i>We spent our days without knowing.</i>

1130
01:03:06,790 --> 01:03:09,649
<i>We spent our days without knowing.</i>

1131
01:03:09,884 --> 01:03:14,076
<i>Like hands on a clock.</i>

1132
01:03:14,311 --> 01:03:17,037
<i>Can you see my tears?</i>

1133
01:03:17,372 --> 01:03:20,380
<i>Can you hear my voice?</i>

1134
01:03:20,815 --> 01:03:28,700
<i>Come hold me who is crying.</i>

1135
01:03:28,725 --> 01:03:31,471
<i>Our breathing... our lips...</i>

1136
01:03:33,006 --> 01:03:34,178
<i>It was connected.</i>

1137
01:03:34,957 --> 01:03:36,638
<i>We were able to ride a rhythm.</i>

1138
01:03:44,965 --> 01:03:48,583
<i>It is the first time I'm playing catch ball with this man.</i>

